Incoming Mail Boxes
	'mailboxes', such as incoming spool pointed to by $MAIL - where mail
	automatically arrives.


Thunderbird setup tasks
	Mail accounts
		Server settings
			check every 10 minutes
			expunge Inbox on Exit
		Folders
			point to IMAP server folders
		Offline & Disk space
			keep only ?
		
	Newsgroup accounts
		Server settings
			check every 90 minutes
		Folders
			point to IMAP server folders
		Offline & Disk space
			keep only unread

